Here´s what you do: Open with deamon tools ( I used version 3.41), press the install button when the menu appears. When the program wants a serial to continue installing type 0901-3324366-4702210-2081 ( worked for me). After installing you will need a nocd crack which you can find here: http://www.gameburnworld.com/dl/gamefixes/dl_blackandwhitecreatureislev1.0nocdfixedexeeng.htm
After downloading it extract with winrar and copy the exe file to the folder where the game is installed and where you find the original exe file(C:ProgramLionhead Studios Ltd, if not anything was changed during installation) and woallah it should be working. Enjoy!
